---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
import EmailLink from "../components/EmailLink.astro"
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Work with me — Matías Baldanza"
  description="Freelance technical content, demos, docs, and consulting from Matías Baldanza."
>
  <header>
    <h1>Work with me</h1>
    <p class="meta">Freelance content &amp; consulting</p>
  </header>

  <p class="subtitle">
    I help developer-tool companies explain what they build — with working demos,
    clear docs, and content developers actually use.
  </p>

  <h2>What I do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Technical writing</strong> — tutorials, guides, release notes, and
      docs that match how developers learn.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Demos &amp; samples</strong> — runnable examples, starter repos,
      and proof that the happy path works.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Workshops &amp; live education</strong> — hands-on sessions for
      mixed skill levels, in English or Spanish.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Per-issue consulting</strong> — bugfixing, architecture review,
      and targeted help on a specific problem (a model I've used for years).
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Background</h2>
  <p>
    Two decades of technical work as a developer, sysadmin, and infrastructure
    engineer; more than ten years producing developer content at native level in
    English and Spanish. I've run daily live-coding streams, taught workshops
    with hundreds of sign-ups, and sustained high-volume video cadences.
  </p>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>
    Email is best: <EmailLink
      label="matiasbaldanza@gmail.com"
      subject="Work with Matías — "
    />. A few sentences about your product, timeline, and what you need is
    enough to start.
  </p>
  <p class="meta">
    Argentina-based, remote, US-hours compatible. I reply within a few business
    days.
  </p>

  <p class="meta back-link">
    <a href="/">← Home</a>
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
